.TH laptop-login 1 "$(date +%Y)" "laptop"
.SH NAME
laptop-login \- run profile login steps (e.g. GitHub auth)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B laptop login
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B laptop login
command runs the profile's
.I login.d
steps in alphabetical order. The default profile includes a GitHub login step which ensures you are authenticated with the GitHub CLI.

.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
laptop login
.fi

.SH SEE ALSO
.BR laptop-setup (1)
